    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "business †",
      "Business Class\nSwitzerland - North America\nBoissons - Beverages\nApéritifs:\nCampari - Rum Bacardi - Dry Sherry Tio Pepe\nBeefeater Dry Martini - Beefeater Dry Gin\nMartini Bianco - Martini Rosso\n- Vodka Smirnoff\nChivas Regal 12 years old - Jack Daniel's old No. 7\nThe Glenlivet aged 12 years\nVins:\nChampagne brut\nVin blanc suisse\nVin blanc français\nDôle sélectionnée\nChâteau Beau-Site\nCru Bourgeois, Saint-Estèphe\nPorto Cockburn's\nWines:\nFrench Champagne Brut\nSwiss white wine\nFrench white wine\nSwiss red wine from the Valais\nBordeaux\nfrom Saint-Estephe\nCockburn's Port\nBière\nBeer\nBière sans alcool «Schlossgold»\nNon-alcoholic beer 'Schlossgold'\nBoissons sans alcool\nNon-alcoholic beverages\nLiqueurs et digestifs:\nBailey's Irish Cream - Calvados V.S.O.P.\nCointreau - Martell V.S.O.P - Drambuie\nKirsch - Poire William - Fernet Branca"
